§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ Let $X$ a finite nonempty set. ⦉

  ‖ A function $f: \powerset{X} → 𝗥$ is ❬submodular❭ if
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ f(S ∪ T) + f(S ∩T) ≤ f(S) + f(T) ⦉
    ⦉
    for all $S, T ⊂ X$. ⦉
⦉

